---

<div class="flex flex-row justify-center align-middle mx-10 space-x-10">
  <div class="text-dark-txt dark:text-light-txt max-w-md lg:max-w-full lg:pt-16 leading-tight text-center lg:justify-start">
    <h3 class="text-lg lg:text-xl font-heading">
      Hi there &#128075; <br />I'm <span class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-orange font-bold"
        >David
      </span>
    </h3>
    <h5>
      I'm an aspiring software engineer. Devoted to building efficient,
      maintainable solutions.
    </h5>
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-center lg:space-x-4">
      <button
        class="bg-blue-dark dark:bg-yellow-bright text-light-txt dark:text-dark font-body font-bold py-3 mt-3 rounded w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 hover:scale-110 hover:translate-y-1 ease-in-out duration-500"
        >Contact me
      </button>
      <button
        class="bg-yellow-dull dark:bg-lavender text-dark font-body font-bold py-3 mt-3 rounded w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 hover:scale-110 hover:translate-y-1 ease-in-out duration-500"
        >View Projects
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-h-[450px] max-w-[450px] hidden lg:block">
    <img
      src="/heroImage.png"
      class="h-full w-full"
      alt="Hero Image. A picture of me looking off into the distance pensively."
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>
</div>
